text: The 1985 Mexico City earthquake was an earthquake that happened in Mexico City on September 19, 1985. It had a magnitude of 8.1, and the number of people killed was around 10,000. ==Related pages== *2017 Puebla earthquake Category:1985 disasters Category:1985 in North America 1985 earthquake Category:Earthquakes in Mexico Category:Earthquakes in the 1980s 1985 earthquake
